<div class="breadcrumb breadcrumbs"><div class="breadcrumb-trail"><a href="http://whatconsumesme.com" title="what consumes me, bud caddell" rel="home" class="trail-begin">Home</a> <span class="sep">&raquo;</span> <a href="http://whatconsumesme.com/2011/" title="2011">2011</a> <span class="sep">&raquo;</span> <a href="http://whatconsumesme.com/category/posts-ive-written/" title="posts i&#039;ve written">posts i've written</a> <span class="sep">&raquo;</span> <span class="trail-end">what is a digital strategy?</span></div></div>
